[gd_scene load_steps=7 format=3]

; A bartending customer = an NPC (bar_customer.gd extends NPC). Mirrors npc.tscn's structure
; (collider + placeholder capsule + NavAgent + Mixamo Animator) but has NO fixed definition or
; dialogue — the shift assigns a random patron NPCDefinition before adding it, and the Animator
; swaps to that model. The placeholder capsule hides once the rigged body builds.

